{Songs:[{Guid:"DVAmykpKc0SzWIlhy14KIQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA MBERE   Isaia 25: 6a, 7, 9</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GUTHOMA IBUKU RIA MURATHI ISAIA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Muthenyaini ucio, kirimaini gikiri, nikuo Mwathani Munene wa Ita akarugithiria nduriri ciothe iruga ria nyama noru.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ni akeheria kindu kiria kihumbite andu a mihirihga </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yothe akininire kirimaini giki hamwa na tama wa kwihumba mutwe uria uthiikiriirie andu a nduririi ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Gikuu ni kungaria aking'aritie agakinina biu tene na tene; ningi Mwathani Ngai ni akagiria maithori mothiu mothe,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na rumena ruria andu ake mamenetwo arunine ruthire thi; tondu Mwathani niwe waritie uhoro ucio. Muthenya ucio ni gukeranwo uu:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Atiriri, uyu niwe Ngai witu, na niwe twetereire atuhonokie.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Uyu ni we Mwathani, na niwe twetereire, ni getha tukene na tucanjamuke ni undu wa kuhonokania gwake.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Iini, Mwathani, aria magaconoka ni migaruka, iria igarukanaga tuhu.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>1. Ririkana matha maku, o nayo mituganire yaku, Mwathani, ni amu ndire yaaga o kuuma tene.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ndirikana kuringana  o na uguo utugi waku utarii, ni undu wa wega waku, wee Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Iini, Mwathani, aria magaconoka ni migaruka, iria igarukanaga tuhu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>2. Kuria ngoro yakwa ihatikiiruo, miaramirie, ukinyumie mitandiukoini iria ndi nayo.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Rora mathina makwa o na uria ndituhiiruo; ukindekere mahitia makwa mothe.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Iini, Mwathani, aria magaconoka ni migaruka, iria igarukanaga tuhu.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>3. Menyagirira ngoro yakwa, ukandeithuragel ndukanareke njonoke, tondu nowe nyagiire.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Wikindiru wa ngoro, o gwata urungiriruri, maundo macio ni mangitagire, amu wee niwe njitagirira.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Iini, Mwathani, aria magaconoka ni migaruka, iria igarukanaga tuhu.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RUIMBO RWA ALLELUYA</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya, Alleluya. Ukani, inyui murathimitwo ni Awa, gwatai igai ria uthamaki uria</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> mwathondekeiruo gwata riria thi yombiruo. Alelluya.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KWA INJIRI</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE MATHAYO:</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io Yesu akiira arumuriri ake: Na riri, riria Muru wa mundu agoka e na riri wake, na araika othe hamwe nake,</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> hindi io ni agaikarira giti giake gia uthamaki kiria kii na riri: na nduriri ciothe ni ikonganio mbere yake: nake ni agaciamurania,</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> o ta uria muriithi aamuranagia ng'ondu na mburi: aige ng'ondu mwena wake wa urio, no mburi aciige wake wa umotho.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Hindi io Muthamaki ni akera aria mari mwena wake wa urio atiri: Ukani, inyui murathimitwo ni Awa,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> gwatai igai ria uthamaki uria mwathondekeiruo gwata riria thi yombiruo: ni gukoruo ndari muhutu, na mukihe irio; </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndari munyotu, na mukihe gia kunyua;</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ndari mugendi, na mukindaaririria kwanyu;</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ndari njaga, na mukihe gia kwihumba;</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ndari muruaru, na mugiuka kundora; ndari korokoro-ini, na mugiuka kuri nii.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io aria athingu ni makamucokeria mamuurie atiri: Mwathani, ni ri twakuonire wi muhutu, tugikuhe irio?</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Kana wi munyotu, tugikuhe gia kunyua? Ningi ni ri twakuonire wi mugendi, tugikuraaririria gwitu? Kana wi njaga, tugikuhe gia kwihumba?</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Na ni ri twakuonire wi muruaru, kana wi korokoroini, na tugiuka kuri wee? Nake Muthamaki ni agacokia amere:</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ngumwira atiri na ma, o ta uria mwekire umwe wa ariu a Awa, o na ari aria anyinyi muno, maundo macio, o uguo ni nii mwekire.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io ni akera aria mari mwena wake wa umotho atiri: Umai kuri nii, inyui mugwatitwo ni kirumi muthii mwaki-ini utahorekaga,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> uria uthondekeiruo mucukana na araika ake: ni gukoruo ndari muhutu, na mut'he irio; ndari munyotu, na mutihe gia kunyua;</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ndari mugendi, na mutindaariririe kwanyu; ndari njaga, na mutihe gia kwihumba; ndari muruaru, na ndari korokoroini, na mutiuke kundora.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io o nao ni magacoka mamuurie atiri: Mwathani ni ri twakuonire wi muhutu, kana wi munyotu,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> kana wi mugendi, kana wi njaga, kana wi muruaru, kana wi korokoroini, na tutigutungatire?</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io ni agacokia amere: Ngumwira atiri na ma, o ta uria mutekire umwe wa acio anyinyi muno maundo macio, o uguo ni nii mutekire.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nao andu acio ni magathii kuria kuherithangario tene na tene: no riri, aria athingu ni magatonya muoyoini wa tene na tene.   </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>     Injiri ya  Mwathani.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"MITHA YA KERI"}],Guid:"O1kmLG1SsEu/1+VmoccW8Q",
Text:"MITHA YA AKUU"}